  "detailed_description": "<strong>Demolition Party is a 4 player PVP car shooter game. Compete to destroy your friendships in the unique collection of maps and guns.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONLINE MULTIPLAYER</strong></h2>Play however you want. Demolition Party allows you to play up to 4 player online multiplayer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/e2854ea6093fa38d44e48eb84a7871eb.poster.avif?t=1712962518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/e2854ea6093fa38d44e48eb84a7871eb.webm?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/e2854ea6093fa38d44e48eb84a7871eb.mp4?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TONS OF GUNS</strong></h2>There are tons of guns for \"demolish\" party and your friendships! :)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/8ff52a50c137cb04768cac4cbe961457.poster.avif?t=1712962518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/8ff52a50c137cb04768cac4cbe961457.webm?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/8ff52a50c137cb04768cac4cbe961457.mp4?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNIQUE MAPS</strong></h2>Compete and fun in unique maps, Don't fall into the lava!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/c01b464b23f67192b97530a5b2fd8fe4.poster.avif?t=1712962518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/c01b464b23f67192b97530a5b2fd8fe4.webm?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/c01b464b23f67192b97530a5b2fd8fe4.mp4?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY WITH AI</strong></h2>Don't have enough friends to play with? No worries! Demolition Party offers the option to play with AI opponents. Sharpen your skills, test your strategies, and have a blast while battling against AI-controlled cars.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Demolition Party is a 4 player PVP car shooter game. Compete to destroy your friendships in the unique collection of maps and guns.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONLINE MULTIPLAYER</strong></h2>Play however you want. Demolition Party allows you to play up to 4 player online multiplayer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/e2854ea6093fa38d44e48eb84a7871eb.poster.avif?t=1712962518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/e2854ea6093fa38d44e48eb84a7871eb.webm?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/e2854ea6093fa38d44e48eb84a7871eb.mp4?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TONS OF GUNS</strong></h2>There are tons of guns for \"demolish\" party and your friendships! :)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/8ff52a50c137cb04768cac4cbe961457.poster.avif?t=1712962518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/8ff52a50c137cb04768cac4cbe961457.webm?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/8ff52a50c137cb04768cac4cbe961457.mp4?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNIQUE MAPS</strong></h2>Compete and fun in unique maps, Don't fall into the lava!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/c01b464b23f67192b97530a5b2fd8fe4.poster.avif?t=1712962518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/c01b464b23f67192b97530a5b2fd8fe4.webm?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172750/extras/c01b464b23f67192b97530a5b2fd8fe4.mp4?t=1712962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY WITH AI</strong></h2>Don't have enough friends to play with? No worries! Demolition Party offers the option to play with AI opponents. Sharpen your skills, test your strategies, and have a blast while battling against AI-controlled cars.",
